These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: brown, apricot, ebony, ivory, blood-red, amber, mauve
House: wooden, cottage, art-deco, modern, ranch-style, cape-cod, colonial
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, golf, skateboarding, surfing, swimming
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, vegafina, dunhill, bolivar, bluemaster, prince, ritmeester
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the modern house##1
 3. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the cottage house is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 5. the wooden house is on the right of the colonial house##1
 6. the person who likes apricot is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 8. the bolivar-smoker is between the ritmeester-smoker and the cape-cod house##2
 9. the ranch-style house is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
10. the person who likes ebony is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who likes blood-red##1
12. the person who likes blood-red is the chaman-smoker##1
13. the person who likes brown is on the left of the art-deco house##1
14. the cape-cod house is the dunhill-smoker##1
15. the prince-smoker is on the left of the colonial house##1
16. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
17. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the art-deco house##1
18. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
19. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Color      | apricot  | amber        | blood-red | ebony      | ivory     | brown      | mauve     |
| House   | cottage | modern         | colonial   | wooden | cape-cod    | ranch-style | art-deco |
